{"tid":1104121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平過車位、萬年死場！元朗錫降圍單位66萬成交！","createTime":"2019-04-13T01:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T02:07:55.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fadb85cf428b0d6037ac57cce2429a8be32d34d","tid":1104121,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T01:55:55.000Z","msg":"忠誠於今日舉行拍賣會，推拍15項物業，並沽出其中1伙，物業為元朗錫降圍單號低層A單位，面積140方呎，開價63萬，屬銀主盤，每口價1萬，獲2組買家爭購，終經4口價，以66萬成交，呎價約4714元。<br />\n<br />\n忠誠拍賣行拍賣部總經理鄭世傑表示，是次拍出單位的質素不俗，而且鄰近車站，又指上址成交價貼近迷你倉及車位的價錢，形容單位甚至「平過車位」，故能成功拍出。<br />\n<br />\n他預料，同場拍賣的同區單位，為雙號B座低層連天台，同屬銀主盤，面積105方呎，開價60萬，有機會可於下場拍賣拍出，惟未必調整其開價。此外，由於受不加息因素影響，買家入市意欲逐漸增強，因此拍賣場上的成交亦將漸漸回升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/976804-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E3%80%90%E9%99%84%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E7%9B%B8%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%8C%AB%E9%99%8D%E5%9C%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%88%B666%E8%90%AC%E6%8B%8D%E5%87%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F976804-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%259B%25B8%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2599%258D%25E5%259C%258D%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%2588%25B666%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%2587%25BA&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=6543977d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F976804-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%259B%25B8%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2599%258D%25E5%259C%258D%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%2588%25B666%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%2587%25BA&h=7804bd77\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/976804-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E3%80%90%E9%99%84%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E7%9B%B8%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%8C%AB%E9%99%8D%E5%9C%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%88%B666%E8%90%AC%E6%8B%8D%E5%87%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n搭程小巴出到天水圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823501f30b99ca5aecbc1e85ffdaee39bcb08c9d","tid":1104121,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"面積105方呎<br />\n<br />\n用黎做迷你倉就差唔多"},{"pid":"60f9cbaeb692dcb99585d4abb7c84bf8a3c5f63e","tid":1104121,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:07:55.000Z","msg":"好過交租"}]}